\id 2TI Matupi Chin Standard Bible
\h 2TIMOTHY
\toc1 2TIMOTHY
\toc2 2Timothy
\toc3 2Ti
\mt1 TIMOTHY CAPAT
\mt3 A Pabae Nah
\mt4 (Second Letter to Timothy)
\is2 TIMOTHY CAPAT PABAE KAWNG
\im Lamhma kah lakah khaw a pabae dongah he Paul loh Timothy amah ham oluennah muep a khueh. Timothy he a oingaih a ca la om tih thangthuinah dongah rhawp a khueh (chapter 1.2,3). Timothy loh muep a ueh dongah Khrih kah rhalkap then la om (2.1,3). Timothy he a manu neh a numca loh mueihla ben ah a rhoengnah hamla a camoe lamloh a tukkil coeng.
\ip Cuekcawnnah dongah aka man cadong caloe rhoek bangla om pawt ham khaw a rhalrhing sak (2.20-26; 3.1-9). Olthangthen thui khaw mah kah mingthennah ham boel saeh lamtah Pathen ram ham saeh (4.2). Te dongah laithae saya rhoek khaw a rhalrhing sak.
\ip Paul loh a dueknah tue khaw laplap a ming, tedae uepomnah thapang khaw anih hamla om coeng (4.6-8), dongah Timothy olrho a pat (2.11,12a).
\iot Sawt Yoeinah
\io1 Timothy kuttuknah neh thangthui nah \ior (1. 1,2)\ior*
\io1 Boeipa ham atah yak boeh \ior (1. 3-18)\ior*
\io1 Khrih kah rhalkap then la om lah \ior (2. 1-26)\ior*
\io1 Khohnin a bawtnah kah hlang khosak \ior (3. 1-9)\ior*
\io1 Uepom la om phat la \ior (3. 10—4. 8)\ior*
\io1 Uennah neh hnukkhueng olrho \ior (4. 9-22)\ior*
